name: Opus III Booster Box
extDescription:
From the multi-million selling FINAL FANTASY franchise comes a brand new trading card experience! This 2-player game has even more cards for you to collect in the Opus III collection, the latest set of FINAL FANTASY TRADING CARDS to be released to the Western market.

Each individual Booster pack includes:
• 12 cards total
• 1 premium foiled card

36 packs per Booster display.
